# Next.js App Router

- Keep `src/app/**/page.tsx` **thin** — delegate to `@/features/*`.
- Use `export const metadata` in server page files when SEO/title matters.
- Default to Server Components; add `'use client'` only when needed (hooks, events, browser APIs).
- Route folders: **kebab-case**. Route groups `(name)/` are optional — see `.agents/app-types.md`.
- For Next.js-specific APIs, prefer docs in `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` when unsure.
